description: Represents the success of a job as returned to the pipeline by a job worker. Used for custom actions only.

parameters.name: jobId
parameters.description: The unique system-generated ID of the job that succeeded. This is the same ID returned from PollForJobs.

parameters.name: currentRevision
parameters.description: The ID of the current revision of the artifact successfully worked on by the job. The revision ID of the current version of an artifact. The change identifier for the current revision. created (datetime) --- The date and time when the most recent revision of the artifact was created, in timestamp format. revisionSummary (string) --- The summary of the most recent revision of the artifact.

nested_params.name: revision
nested_params.description: The revision ID of the current version of an artifact.

nested_params.name: changeIdentifier
nested_params.description: The change identifier for the current revision.

nested_params.name: created
nested_params.description: The date and time when the most recent revision of the artifact was created, in timestamp format.

nested_params.name: revisionSummary
nested_params.description: The summary of the most recent revision of the artifact.

parameters.name: executionDetails
parameters.description: The execution details of the successful job, such as the actions taken by the job worker. summary (string) --- The summary of the current status of the actions. externalExecutionId (string) --- The system-generated unique ID of this action used to identify this job worker in any external systems, such as CodeDeploy. percentComplete (integer) --- The percentage of work completed on the action, represented on a scale of 0 to 100 percent.

nested_params.name: summary
nested_params.description: The summary of the current status of the actions.

nested_params.name: externalExecutionId
nested_params.description: The system-generated unique ID of this action used to identify this job worker in any external systems, such as CodeDeploy.

nested_params.name: percentComplete
nested_params.description: The percentage of work completed on the action, represented on a scale of 0 to 100 percent.

parameters.name: outputVariables
parameters.description: Key-value pairs produced as output by a job worker that can be made available to a downstream action configuration. outputVariables can be included only when there is no continuation token on the request. (string) --- (string) ---
